{"tid":904901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳大橋業務拖累     冠忠巴士發盈警料少賺六成","createTime":"2018-11-16T17:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T02:34:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d5db2d1664204efff012fd0144703e822fa86cf5","tid":904901,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:09:49.000Z","msg":"冠忠巴士（0306）發盈警，預期截至今年9月底止中期純利將不多於4000萬元，意味上半年純利將大跌超過六成。集團解釋，上半年盈利大跌，除因為欠缺出售資產的特殊收益、油價推升成本外，集團期內因港珠澳大橋開通開展跨境巴士業務造成巨大開支，亦是盈警主因之一。<br />\n<br />\n冠忠表示，港珠澳大橋開業成本包括採購額外巴士產生較大的折舊支出、租用跨境巴士配額、司機招聘、培訓以及宣傳開支等；同時集團去年上半年因出售錄得5900萬元非經常性收益，推高基數下令今年上半年收益按年下滑。<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋上月開通，在大量過境遊客湧入在東涌造成交通擠塞及混亂，冠忠主席黃良柏早前曾現身「護航」，表示不應單看一天或一個月的情況，相信有關路線將會大受市民歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1542380558709&amp;issue=20181116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1542380558709%26issue%3D20181116&d=6c610CMsiqVX8lnycmZZXwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=6ab278f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1542380558709&amp;issue=20181116</a>"},{"pid":"c98a11cf3da690bb45832fca46f646af51ae2ae4","tid":904901,"uid":31946,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:11:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾冠忠最好執柒左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9a6bd99bd80a052ea9b285af5987216d11c14f","tid":904901,"uid":6799,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:33:19.000Z","msg":"奶共奶到執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2029533a2a0294e70bd9a85d5111b4d089fbf0c5","tid":904901,"uid":46896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:35:02.000Z","msg":"抵死啦無良柏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347cb9e6